Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有落叶了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明早打扫又够呛了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.98,0:00:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边也够呛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有什么我能做的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.62,0:00:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小鸠姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.40,0:00:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.13,0:00:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.66,0:00:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起出门去了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.81,0:00:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这两个孩子的学校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.56,0:00:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在商量义卖会的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.85,0:00:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义卖会？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都会带着各种各样的东西来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.38,0:01:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后卖掉  把钱用在学校上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.94,0:01:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
